title: Emprox Oceanic Challenger Series Roster Announcement!

embed.description: Emprox is proud to announce the Oceanic Challenger Series roster for 2018! Their Journey starts tonight! Top Doudou Jungle Wai Middle @SanctumChazz Marksman @Farmer_OCE Support @lolKohta Manager @edisudev Coach @222_2_555_33_22 Analyst @Erebus45258 https://t.co/etFm2cgH4q

body:
Emprox announces its League of Legends lineup for the Oceanic Challenger Series ahead of matches in Week 1 of the 13 weeks split!
There are some old but some new names that will represent the balance of experience and talent for the lineup.
